decks.notes: The deck focuses on fast and disruptive strategies to control the game while deploying threats quickly. It utilizes powerful artifacts like Mishra's Workshop and Ancient Tomb to accelerate mana production and overwhelm opponents with cheap threats like Stonecoil Serpent and Patchwork Automaton. It also includes disruptive elements like Sphere of Resistance and Thorn of Amethyst to slow down opponents' plays, while also utilizing cards like Karn, the Great Creator and Crucible of Worlds for additional utility and recursion. Overall, the deck aims to quickly establish board presence and disrupt opponent strategies to secure a victory.
